Wrote Python script "check_hrt_atlas_enst_to_ensg_mapping.py" on 20.05.26 to check whether the reduction from the original HRT Atlas Transcript ID list to fewer unique Ensembl Gene Stable IDs is caused by missing BioMart mappings or by multiple transcripts mapping to the same gene.
